description: Contains some simple and commonly used WPF controls based on HandyControl
releaseNotes:
Add AutoCompleteTextBox
Add HighlightTextBlock
Add DataGrid.Small style
Add RadioButtonSameAsButton style
Add Support for Validation (hc:TextBox, hc:ComboBox, hc:CheckComboBox, hc:NumericUpDown, hc:DateTimePicker, hc:DatePicker, hc:TimePicker, input elements)
Add Spanish Language
Upgraded waterfallpanel
Upgraded UniformSpacingPanel
BlurWindows Now Works on all Windows 10 Builds
Optimized UniformSpacingPanel
Modified ScrollBar style
Modified popup HorizontalOffset
Modified Datagrid style (RowHeight, ColumnHeaderHeight, ShowSelectAllButton)
Avoid duplicated ResourceDictionary
Update ListClock Content Alignment
Fixed colorpicker will crashed when SelectedBrush prop assigned to null
Fixed PersianCalendar Month Names Style
Fixed [Issue #890](https://github.com/HandyOrg/HandyControl/issues/890)
Fixed [Issue #903](https://github.com/HandyOrg/HandyControl/issues/903)

Fixed [Issue #913](https://github.com/HandyOrg/HandyControl/issues/913)
Fixed [Issue #81](https://github.com/ghost1372/HandyControls/issues/81)
